  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "OPERATIONS MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an experienced and reliable Operations Manager to lead our hotel operations during night shifts and weekends. The successful candidate must have at least 5 years of hands-on operations experience in hotels in Singapore. This role is essential in ensuring smooth operations, guest satisfaction, and staff supervision during non-standard hours.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>l Manage and oversee all hotel operations during night shifts and weekends.</p><p>l Lead and support night shift teams, including Front Office, Housekeeping, F&B, and Security.</p><p>l Ensure smooth check-in/check-out processes and address guest needs or complaints promptly.</p><p>l Handle night audits and ensure accurate reporting of daily revenue and occupancy figures.</p><p>l Monitor service quality, cleanliness, and safety across the hotel.</p><p>l Respond to emergencies, handle incidents, and coordinate with relevant departments.</p><p>l Ensure handover of all important matters to the day team for continuity.</p><p>l Uphold company standards and ensure compliance with Singapore’s hotel regulations.</p><p>l Train and guide night staff to maintain high service standards.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>l Minimum 5 years of hotel operations experience in Singapore is mandatory.</p><p>l Proven track record of managing night shifts and weekend operations.</p><p>l Strong leadership, communication, and problem-solving skills.</p><p>l Good knowledge of local hospitality regulations and service standards.</p><p>l Proficiency in hotel property management systems (e.g., Opera, Fidelio).</p><p>l Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management or related field preferred.</p><p>l Able to work independently and make decisions during critical situations.</p><p>We thank you for your interest and we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. All resumes received will be used for recruitment purposes only.</p><p>EA License ID: 18C9520</p><p>EA Registration ID: R1765753</p>",
